  "answer": "B) ربط = ( Anal = internal ) حرف n مع n .\nLateral internal sphincterotomy is an operation performed on the internal anal sphincter muscle for the treatment of chronic anal fissure. The internal anal sphincter is one of two muscles that comprise the anal sphincter which controls the passage of fece",
