  "question": "325-18 year old healthy male was playing baseball and suddenly he felt abdominal pain. On  examination he has para-umbilical mass. His vital signs Bp 100/76 RR 30 HR 100 O2 sat.  95% oxygen mask. What is your(( next)) step in management?",
