  "question": "Patient has hx of RTA since 2 weeks came today with SOB the chest x ray has shown haemothorax you have put him on chest tube and want to transfer him to higher center while he was in the ambulance the pulse oximetry drop suddenly what to do ?\n![Image](images/review_bank/515158176-Surgery-2020-with-correction-docx-docx-docx_23.jpg)",
