  "question": "Pancreatitis 5 weeks ago. Now she has epigastric tenderness and cannot tolerate food with vomiting each time. By ultrasound you found large about 12X10 mass With thick wall and fluid inside. Labs: 346 amylase, Wbc 15k. What is the diagnosis?",
